ji\" /> <br />\n有啲戰鬥力唔代表值得放上神枱喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係話要上神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年冇隻打得，想搵D野吹奏下啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2d4a9f047f2a7c27ccbd43bac972153c466e79","tid":379018,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}